strings.Value: "Do not be set aback by how quietly I keep to my thoughts. Come to me and I will discuss with you the frailty of life, the whisper of the night, the great god..."
"'Quietly keep your thoughts?' You mean how you act like a coffin stuffer? No thanks!"
"Certainly, I'll talk to you. I don't think we'll influence each other's opinion... But that doesn't mean we shouldn't try, right?"
"There's something funny about your incessant gloominess. I'll be happy to take you up on your offer. â€” After all, I need to understand you well, so I can depict you accurately in my book!"
